name: executorRunTime
description: Elapsed time the executor spent running this task. This includes time fetching shuffle data.

name: executorCpuTime
description: CPU time the executor spent running this task. This includes time fetching shuffle data.

name: executorDeserializeTime
description: Elapsed time spent to deserialize this task

name: executorDeserializeCpuTime
description: CPU time taken on the executor to deserialize this task.

name: resultSerializationTime
description: Elapsed time spent serializing the task result.

name: jvmGCTime
description: Elapsed time the JVM spent in garbage collection while executing this task.
